28. Determine what value gets printed out without using a computer.
    Choose the correct answer from 0, 100, 101, 517, or 1000.

    int cnt = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++)
       for (int j = 0; j < 10; j++)
          for (int k = 0; k < 10; k++)
             if (2*i + j >= 3*k)
                cnt++;
    System.out.println(cnt);

    i  j  k  cnt  out
    0  0  0  1
          1
       1  0  2
          1
       2  0  3
          1
       3  0  4
          1  5
          2
       4  0  6
          1  7
          2

    A: 517

